When we arrived we were greeted by an exceptionally friendly valet - this was a pattern as all of the valets we interacted with were friendly and helpful, as were the reception staff.	Be aware that parking is by valet at additional cost but is quick and the service is as friendly as every other department in this property.	Not only did they leave chocolates and wine in the room for us, the housekeeping staff was pleasant and well trained and the valet staff was polite and courteous.	Not once during our stay did the gentlemen working the valet open the door for us and greet us.